{"tid":2366892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紐約時報：巴西調低中國科興疫苗有效率，意味著什麼？","createTime":"2021-01-15T02:16:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T08:05:01.000Z","uid":319512,"like":41,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"5670dac0c1cd678431906d7dac6068329a5f9d3b","tid":2366892,"uid":319512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T02:16:35.000Z","msg":"&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n與其他疫苗不同的是，中國科興CoronaVac採用的是比較舊的技術，該技術使用化學物質來減弱或殺死病毒，然後將其放入疫苗，以在接種者體內激發抗體。但是殺死病毒的過程會削弱疫苗的效力，導致免疫反應的時間縮短或降低。<br />\n<br />\n「這是美國人和歐洲人沒有採用這種較老技術的原因之一。」康乃爾大學疫苗專家約翰&middot;摩爾(John Moore)說。「一輛維護得不錯的福特老爺車也能從武漢開到北京，但我個人會選擇特斯拉。」<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip; <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f7fc3173831f99aca371ce75edd14fd1d1a5144","tid":2366892,"uid":319512,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5670dac0c1cd678431906d7dac6068329a5f9d3b","tid":2366892,"uid":319512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T02:16:35.000Z","msg":"&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n與其他疫苗不同的是，中國科興CoronaVac採用的是比較舊的技術，該技術使用化學物質來減弱或殺死病毒，然後將其放入疫苗，以在接種者體內激發抗體。但是殺死病毒的過程會削弱疫苗的效力，導致免疫反應的時間縮短或降低。<br />\n<br />\n「這是美國人和歐洲人沒有採用這種較老技術的原因之一。」康乃爾大學疫苗專家約翰&middot;摩爾(John Moore)說。「一輛維護得不錯的福特老爺車也能從武漢開到北京，但我個人會選擇特斯拉。」<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip; <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T02:17:07.000Z","msg":"原文Link<br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.nytimes.com/business/20210114/chinese-vaccine-brazil-sinovac/zh-hant/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.nytimes.com%2Fbusiness%2F20210114%2Fchinese-vaccine-brazil-sinovac%2Fzh-hant%2F&d=qXcR1A%2FTALq%2FhnoNE0cJVUVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=06354f96\" target=\"_blank\">https://cn.nytimes.com/business/20210114/chinese-vaccine-brazil-sinovac/zh-hant/</a>"},{"pid":"29de3ae3a10d9dbbc6d3412d7359bd4ea42f5c1e","tid":2366892,"uid":295230,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T02:18:10.000Z","msg"